{
  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view captures a vibrant fireworks display over a sprawling city skyline and a long bridge stretching across dark water. The fireworks explode in a brilliant burst of red, white, and gold, dominating the upper-left portion of the frame. Below, a long, illuminated bridge with numerous lights extends horizontally, leading towards a city filled with illuminated buildings, creating a sense of depth. The city itself is a tapestry of lights, with tall structures standing out against the dark sky. The water reflects some of the lights, adding to the overall luminescence. The scene evokes a festive and celebratory atmosphere.",
